    <headline>Frequent lightning, yellow level, Nordmøre, Trøndelag and parts of Nordland, 2022-08-03T11:00:00+00:00, 2022-08-03T18:30:00+00:00</headline>
    <description>There is a risk of frequent lightning. The lightning  will first start in Nordmøre and Trøndelag and then move northwards. There will be large local differences in intensity. Some places will not experience any lightning. </description>
    <instruction>Stay up to date on the development of the weather and the weather forecast. Monitor the weather radar or lyn.met.no. Disconnect electrical appliances. Adjust driving speed according to the road/weather conditions. Seek shelter. Avoid open plains and large trees. Do not swim or bathe. </instruction>
